      <title>费城艺术学院因欠 5000 万美元市政债券而关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/philadelphia-arts-college-with-50-million-of-muni-debt-to-shut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城艺术大学是一所私立大学，专门培养未来的动画师和舞蹈家，目前该校背负着约 5000 万美元的市政债务，由于财务状况恶化，该校即将突然关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/philadelphia-arts-college-with-50-million-of-muni-debt-to-shut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 15:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
