      <title>Chatham Asset 敦促 Sinclair 避免激进的再融资交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/chatham-asset-urges-sinclair-to-sidestep-aggressive-refinancing-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chatham Asset Management 自称是 Sinclair Inc. 最大的债权人之一，它敦促该广播公司抵制分割贷款人抵押品以为即将到期的债务进行再融资的举动。]]></description>
